{"tid":2430774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"四成受訪者評林鄭零分","createTime":"2021-03-03T07:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T08:17:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"600c15e99531e77e41f7846b1847e56b13b197b0","tid":2430774,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:19:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/OD4KIWHZPVHKFELORA26J7Q7BQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FOD4KIWHZPVHKFELORA26J7Q7BQ%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=ce60dec8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FOD4KIWHZPVHKFELORA26J7Q7BQ%2F&h=416e4eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/OD4KIWHZPVHKFELORA26J7Q7BQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n四成受訪者評林鄭零分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fqz3aa17lULSLCrSq6enblfjwWU=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VTT4UJGKDRAZXEGPF2IFV3PHDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFqz3aa17lULSLCrSq6enblfjwWU%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVTT4UJGKDRAZXEGPF2IFV3PHDM.jpg&h=14112c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港民意研究所公佈最新民調，特首林鄭月娥最新評分為33.9分，較2月初高2.9分，但仍有近四成受訪市民給予零分。民研副行政總裁鍾劍華指，在普遍政府民望有回升之際，仍有四成受訪者給予林鄭零分，反映他們對林鄭有「敵意」。<br />\n<br />\n民研在政府公佈財政預算案、警方仍未要求民主派初選者提早報到期間，就特首及政府民望進行調查。結果顯示林鄭最新評分為33.9分，較上次調查高2.9分，更是自前年6月初反修例運動以來新高；細分之下， 林鄭支持率有23%，反對率67%，民望淨值負43個百分點，比上次調查升9個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者︰市民敵意難改<br />\n<br />\n政府民望方面，市民對政府評分稍有回升。民調顯示，市民對政府最新滿意率有23%，不滿意率56%，較上次調查跌5個百分點，滿意率淨值為負33個百分點，比上次調查顯著上升12個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n鍾劍華認為，有關數字上升「唔係特別值得高興」，特別在政府、特首民望數字均有回升，仍有近四成受訪者給予林鄭零分，反映香港部份市民對林鄭產生敵意，難以改觀。<br />\n<br />\n民研主席及行政總裁鍾庭耀估計，調查剛好在預算案出台期間進行，或影響民調結果，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"94c13a05776813a1dbb1f757b8eb826eb307bbdc","tid":2430774,"uid":32081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:21:39.000Z","msg":"從前我滿分 但今天已扣分<br />\n避不開一直寵愛你十個女生"},{"pid":"8e6fd615f6708dd632cc87107186fd9b823052d7","tid":2430774,"uid":254745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">佢都唔撚在乎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883a955b70e1eba88b7276d06c8061a64bae0f97","tid":2430774,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"有駐港解放軍，負分都仲生勾勾"},{"pid":"a93b531b9ebd247121ffcbd744017b88681ed5fe","tid":2430774,"uid":279298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"四成受訪者犯左國安法，比零分即係反政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e75fcd0c95688c317afbbb4128f36654deb2e8","tid":2430774,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:25:54.000Z","msg":"民調仲可以做幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43266be364f40080296450b3f99899c5fe8f503","tid":2430774,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"四成咁少"},{"pid":"3bcd9d955b7a48964a667a5fd8be7fb3838c214b","tid":2430774,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"我畀負十億"},{"pid":"3247032c16edb77fe8d03289002c7e47bf235d6d","tid":2430774,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f43266be364f40080296450b3f99899c5fe8f503","tid":2430774,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"四成咁少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:15:26.000Z","msg":"有時真係好無奈，居然仲有6成人唔係畀零分，我當1成人係共產黨治下的既得利益者，仲有個5成係咪腦裝屎。"},{"pid":"0f3b3ab37f35902cba7de31b92352cd717b559e3","tid":2430774,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite